PS: Our utility stocking platform will be live a few days after mint.

(8/8) If you unstock your Sneakerhead you will not receive any benefits though and you are not eligible for any of the benefits that people stocking receive regardless of what milestone you reached before unstocking.

(7/8) What happens if I stop stocking?

As soon as you stop stocking you will lose all your progress up to your most recent milestone, for example, if you reach stocking level 2 your Sneakerhead will stay at level 2 even if you unstock it.

(6/8) Do I get more benefits if I stock multiple sneakerheads? 

You will get benefits multiplied by the number of Sneakerheads you have. So as a hypothetical example if you have 2 Sneakerheads and stock both for x amount of time you would receive 2 rewards.

(5/8) What kind of benefits will I receive for stocking? 


Benefits will include limited-edition drops, Access to IRL events, airdrops, and much more. Think of stocking like a loyalty program. The longer you stock, the greater the rewards.
(4/8)  Stocking will unlock time-based rewards. The longer you stock your sneakerheads, the more benefits you accumulate.
